snippet.title: First Person Age of Empires? (First look at Overreign Alpha Release)
snippet.description:
Introducing the Overreign Alpha Version which converts age of empires into a first person game. 

Shoutout to Spriteblood for coming up with this version of AoE! Go subscribe to his channel for more updates: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGzJ7MwlrRju0LVTK_bNmNg

Link to download: https://www.dropbox.com/s/y4rgyejj3uxk1xf/Overreign.zip?dl=1

Reddit thread: https://www.reddit.com/r/aoe2/comments/b4avj2/overreign_first_person_aoe2_alpha_release/
